```

### Recommended VS Code Extensions:
- Flutter (already installed âœ…)
- Dart (already installed âœ…) 
- Bloc (for BLoC snippets)
- GitLens (for Git integration)

## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues & Solutions:

#### Issue: "flutter command not found"
```bash
echo 'export PATH="$HOME/development/flutter/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc
```

#### Issue: Package version conflicts
```bash
flutter clean
flutter pub get
```

#### Issue: Analysis errors
```bash
flutter analyze --write=analysis_output.txt
# Review and fix issues listed in the output
```

## Project Status Check

After completing this guide, verify your setup:

âœ… Project created in `~/src/repos/flutter_task_manager/`  
âœ… All dependencies installed without errors  
âœ… Project structure follows Clean Architecture  
